						<summary>

						<p>Fragment of a slab near a well in Survey No. 25/1.</p>						

						<p>This undated epigraph may be assigned to the 16th century on the basis of palaeography.</p>						

						<p>Fragmentary and damaged. It seems to record the apportionment of gift land probably to the excavators of the well. Among the boundaries of the gift-land <hi rend="italic">beḍiga-mānya</hi> is refered to some individuals.</p>						

						</summary>
